gov.loc.mets

Class FileType

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.loc.mets.FileType

  • public class FileType
extends java.lang.Object
    fileType: Complex Type for Files The file element provides access to content files for a METS object. A file element may contain one or more FLocat elements, which provide pointers to a content file, and/or an FContent element, which wraps an encoded version of the file. Note that ALL FLocat and FContent elements underneath a single file element should identify/contain identical copies of a single file.

    Java class for fileType complex type.
